MERGE INTO #SCHEMA.SY#.F00950 t
USING (
  SELECT :FSSETY AS FSSETY,
         :FSUSER AS FSUSER,
         :FSOBNM AS FSOBNM,
         :FSDTAI AS FSDTAI,
         :FSFRDV AS FSFRDV,
         :FSSY AS FSSY,
         :FSOWDI AS FSOWDI,
         :FSFMNM AS FSFMNM,
         :FSFUNO AS FSFUNO,
         :FSINSL AS FSINSL,
         :FSRUN AS FSRUN,
         :FSVWYN AS FSVWYN,
         :FSA AS FSA,
         :FSCHNG AS FSCHNG,
         :FSDLT AS FSDLT,
         :FSTHDV AS FSTHDV,
         :FSOBID AS FSOBID,
         :FSADDC AS FSADDC,
         :FSIOK AS FSIOK,
         :FSICPY AS FSICPY,
         :FSIUPT AS FSIUPT,
         :FSATN1 AS FSATN1,
         :FSATN2 AS FSATN2,
         :FSATN3 AS FSATN3,
         :FSMUSE AS FSMUSE,
         :FSPID AS FSPID,
         :FSJOBN AS FSJOBN,
         :FSUPMJ AS FSUPMJ,
         :FSUPMT AS FSUPMT,
         :FSEXITID AS FSEXITID,
         :FSTABID AS FSTABID,
         :FSTEXTID AS FSTEXTID,
         :FSPTH AS FSPTH
  FROM dual) src
ON (t.FSSETY = src.FSSETY 
    AND t.FSUSER = src.FSUSER 
    AND t.FSOBNM = src.FSOBNM 
    AND t.FSDTAI = src.FSDTAI 
    AND t.FSFRDV = src.FSFRDV 
    AND t.FSSY = src.FSSY)
WHEN MATCHED THEN
  UPDATE SET t.FSOWDI = src.FSOWDI,
             t.FSFMNM = src.FSFMNM,
             t.FSFUNO = src.FSFUNO,
             t.FSINSL = src.FSINSL,
             t.FSRUN = src.FSRUN,
             t.FSVWYN = src.FSVWYN,
             t.FSA = src.FSA,
             t.FSCHNG = src.FSCHNG,
             t.FSDLT = src.FSDLT,
             t.FSTHDV = src.FSTHDV,
             t.FSOBID = src.FSOBID,
             t.FSADDC = src.FSADDC,
             t.FSIOK = src.FSIOK,
             t.FSICPY = src.FSICPY,
             t.FSIUPT = src.FSIUPT,
             t.FSATN1 = src.FSATN1,
             t.FSATN2 = src.FSATN2,
             t.FSATN3 = src.FSATN3,
             t.FSMUSE = UPPER(src.FSMUSE),
             t.FSPID = src.FSPID,
             t.FSJOBN = src.FSJOBN,
             t.FSUPMJ = src.FSUPMJ,
             t.FSUPMT = src.FSUPMT,
             t.FSEXITID = src.FSEXITID,
             t.FSTABID = src.FSTABID,
             t.FSTEXTID = src.FSTEXTID,
             t.FSPTH = src.FSPTH
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
  INSERT (FSSETY, FSUSER, FSOBNM, FSDTAI, FSFRDV, FSSY, FSOWDI, FSFMNM, FSFUNO, FSINSL, FSRUN, FSVWYN, FSA, FSCHNG, FSDLT, FSTHDV, FSOBID, FSADDC, FSIOK, FSICPY, FSIUPT, FSATN1, FSATN2, FSATN3, FSMUSE, FSPID, FSJOBN, FSUPMJ, FSUPMT, FSEXITID, FSTABID, FSTEXTID, FSPTH)
  VALUES (src.FSSETY, src.FSUSER, src.FSOBNM, src.FSDTAI, src.FSFRDV, src.FSSY, src.FSOWDI, src.FSFMNM, src.FSFUNO, src.FSINSL, src.FSRUN, src.FSVWYN, src.FSA, src.FSCHNG, src.FSDLT, src.FSTHDV, src.FSOBID, src.FSADDC, src.FSIOK, src.FSICPY, src.FSIUPT, src.FSATN1, src.FSATN2, src.FSATN3, UPPER(src.FSMUSE), src.FSPID, src.FSJOBN, src.FSUPMJ, src.FSUPMT, src.FSEXITID, src.FSTABID, src.FSTEXTID, src.FSPTH)

SELECT 
  DRDL01 DL01,
  DRKY KY,
  DRRT RT,
  DRSY SY,
  CASE 
    WHEN DRKY IN ('1', '3', '5', '9') THEN 'OBJECTS'
    WHEN DRKY IN ('2', '4', 'B') THEN 'ALIAS'
    ELSE 'OTHERS' END SEC_TYPE 
FROM 
  F0005
WHERE
  DRSY = '98'
  AND DRRT = 'TY'

WITH userRole AS
(
SELECT 
  ABALPH ALPH,
  ULUSER USER_ROLE
FROM
  #SCHEMA.SY#.F0092
LEFT JOIN
  #SCHEMA.DTA#.F0101
  ON ABAN8 = ULAN8
WHERE
  ULUGRP <> '*GROUP'
UNION ALL
SELECT 
  TRIM(AUUSER) USER_ROLE,
  AUROLEDESC ALPH
FROM
  #SCHEMA.SY#.F00926
)
SELECT 
    TRIM(FSSETY) FSSETY,
    CASE 
      WHEN TRIM(FSSETY) IN ('1', '3', '5', '9') THEN 'OBJECTS'
      WHEN TRIM(FSSETY) IN ('2', '4', 'B') THEN 'ALIAS'
      WHEN TRIM(FSSETY) NOT IN ('1', '3', '5', '9', '2', '4', 'B') THEN 'OTHERS'
    END SEC_TYPE,
    FSUSER,
    ALPH,
    TRIM(FSOBNM) FSOBNM ,
    TRIM(FSDTAI) FSDTAI ,
    TRIM(FSFRDV) FSFRDV ,
    TRIM(FSSY) FSSY,
    FSOWDI,
    FSFMNM,
    FSFUNO,
    FSINSL,
    FSRUN,
    FSVWYN,
    FSA,
    FSCHNG,
    FSDLT,
    FSTHDV,
    FSOBID,
    FSADDC,
    FSIOK,
    FSICPY,
    FSIUPT,
    FSATN1,
    FSATN2,
    FSATN3,
    FSMUSE,
    FSPID,
    FSJOBN,
    FSUPMJ,
    FSUPMT,
    FSEXITID,
    FSTABID,
    FSTEXTID,
    FSPTH 
FROM 
  #SCHEMA.SY#.F00950
LEFT JOIN
  userRole
  ON FSUSER = USER_ROLE
